value.original_name: Cheyenne Cinnamon and the Fantabulous Unicorn of Sugar Town Candy Fudge
value.overview: Cheyenne Cinnamon and the Fantabulous Unicorn of Sugar Town Candy Fudge, is an American animated television series created by Dave Willis and computer animated by Radical Axis. The pilot episode aired in the United States on Cartoon Network's late night programming block, Adult Swim on March 29, 2010. The pilot was not picked up for a full series. The pilot was rated TV-MA
